      • verifySignature

        public boolean verifySignature​(PublicKey publicKey)
                        throws org.bouncycastle.cms.CMSException,
                               org.bouncycastle.operator.OperatorCreationException
        This method verifies the signature of the PKCS#7 wrapper of this message.
        Parameters:
        publicKey - the public key of the keypair that signed this message
        Returns:
        true if signature verifies.
        Throws:
        org.bouncycastle.cms.CMSException - if the underlying byte array of this SCEP message couldn't be read
        org.bouncycastle.operator.OperatorCreationException - if a signature verifier couldn't be constructed from the given public key
